<concept id="smoothmeshconvert" xml:lang="en-US">
   <title id="title__Toc50995634">SMOOTHMESHCONVERT System Variable</title>
   <conbody>
      <section><title>Mesh conversion mode</title><p>Specifies mesh to 3d solid or surface conversion mode, used by commands CONVTOSOLID or CONVTOSURFACE. Currently we support conversion only to faceted models, so values 0 and 1, corresponding to conversion to smooth models, are not accessible.</p><p><table id="table_r32_ncz_hnb">
               <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" />
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*" />
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/type" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/short" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/saved_in" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/not_saved" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/range" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>2 to 3</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/default_value" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>2</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/possible_values" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>2: Conversion result is faceted and optimized</p>
                           <p>3: Conversion result is faceted and not optimized</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table></p></section>
   </conbody>
</concept>
